Parameter estimation:

library('DIRECT')
#some settings and initial conditions
D=30            #documents number
N=100           #words number per document(set the same w.l.g)
K=10            #total topic number
V=100           #size of alphabet
niter=50       #number of outer iteration
niniter=10      #number of inner iteration
w=array(0,dim=c(D,N,V))
phi=array(1/K,dim=c(D,N,K))
bet=matrix(sample(1:3,K*V,replace=T),K,V)
for(i in 1:K){
  bet[i,]=bet[i,]/sum(bet[i,])
 # bet[i,10*(i-1)+1:10]=0.1
}
gamm=array(0,dim=c(D,K))
alph=sample(2:4,K,replace=T)
set.seed(10)
doctop=array(0,dim=c(D,3))
for(d in 1:D){
  gamm[d,]=alph+N/K
  doctop[d,]=sample(1:K,3)
  for(n in 1:N){
    a=sample(1:3,1)
    b=sample(10*(doctop[d,a]-1)+1:10,1)
    w[d,n,b]=1
  }
}

# begin parameter estimation
#E-step
for(iter in 1:niter){
  for(d in 1:D){
    for(n in 1:N){
      for(i in 1:K){
        phi[d,n,i]=bet[i,which(w[d,n,]==1)]*exp(digamma(gamm[d,i]))
      }
      phi[d,n,]=phi[d,n,]/sum(phi[d,n,])
    }
    gamm[d,]=alph+colSums(phi[d,,])
  }
  #M-step
  for(i in 1:K){
    for(j in 1:V){
      bet[i,j]=0
      for(d in 1:D){
        for(n in 1:N){
          bet[i,j]=bet[i,j]+phi[d,n,i]*w[d,n,j]
        }
      }
    }
    bet[i,]=bet[i,]/sum(bet[i,])
  }
  temp=rep(0,K)
  L=rep(0,K)
  for(d in 1:D) temp=temp+digamma(gamm[d,])-digamma(sum(gamm[d,]))
  for(initer in 1:niniter){
  L=D*(digamma(sum(alph))-digamma(alph))+temp
  h=-D*trigamma(alph)
  z=D*trigamma(sum(alph))
  c=sum(L/h)/(z^(-1)+sum(h^(-1)))
  alph=alph-0.5*(L-c)/h
  }
}
plot(1:V,bet[10,],type="l")

for(i in 1:K){
  print(paste('The',i,'th row of beta with probability larger than 4e-2:'))
  print(which(bet[i,]>4e-2))
}

## [1]  6 10  7
D=30            #documents number
N=100           #words number per document(set the same w.l.g)
K=10            #total topic number
V=100 
w=array(0,dim=c(D,N,V))
set.seed(10)
doctop=array(0,dim=c(D,3))
for(d in 1:D){
  doctop[d,]=sample(1:K,3)
  for(n in 1:N){
    a=sample(1:3,1)
    b=sample(10*(doctop[d,a]-1)+1:10,1)
    w[d,n,b]=1
  }
}


alph=1
bet=1
iter=100
w_new=matrix(0,N,V)
for(i in 1:N){
  a=sample(c(1,3,7),1)
  w_new[i,sample(10*(a-1)+1:10,1)]=1
}
NK=array(0,dim=c(K,V))
NKS=array(0,dim=c(K))
NM=array(0,dim=c(D,K))
NMS=rep(0,D)
Z=array(0,dim=c(D,N))
for(d in 1:D){
  for(n in 1:N){
    k=sample(1:K,1)
    Z[d,n]=k
    NM[d,k]=NM[d,k]+1
    NMS[d]=NMS[d]+1
    NK[k,which(w[d,n,]==1)]=NK[k,which(w[d,n,]==1)]+1
    NKS[k]=NKS[k]+1
  }
}
for(i in 1:iter){
  for(d in 1:D){
    for(n in 1:N){
      p=rep(0,K)
      k=Z[d,n]
      NM[d,k]=NM[d,k]-1
      NMS[d]=NMS[d]-1
      NK[k,which(w[d,n,]==1)]=NK[k,which(w[d,n,]==1)]-1
      NKS[k]=NKS[k]-1
      for(kk in 1:K){
        p[kk]=(NK[kk,which(w[d,n,]==1)]+bet)*(NM[d,kk]+alph)/(sum(NK[kk,]+bet))
      }
      p=p/sum(p)
      k_new=sample(1:K,1,prob=p)
      Z[d,n]=k_new
      NM[d,k_new]=NM[d,k_new]+1
      NMS[d]=NMS[d]+1
      NK[k_new,which(w[d,n,]==1)]=NK[k_new,which(w[d,n,]==1)]+1
      NKS[k_new]=NKS[k_new]+1
    }
  }
}
phi=array(0,dim=c(K,V))
theta=array(0,dim=c(D,K))
for(k in 1:K){
  for(t in 1:V){
    phi[k,t]=(NK[k,t]+bet)/sum(NK[k,]+bet)
  }
}
for(d in 1:D){
  for(k in 1:K){
    theta[d,k]=(NM[d,k]+a)/sum(NM[d,]+a)
  }
}
plot(1:V,phi[2,])

plot(1:V,phi[3,])

library('DIRECT')
#some settings and initial conditions
D=20            #documents number
N=100           #words number per document(set the same w.l.g)
K=10            #total topic number
V=100           #size of alphabet
niter=100       #number of outer iteration
niniter=10      #number of inner iteration
w=array(0,dim=c(D,N,V))
phi=array(1/K,dim=c(D,N,K))
gamm=array(0,dim=c(D,K))
set.seed(3)
doctop=array(0,dim=c(D,3))
for(d in 1:D){
  doctop[d,]=sample(1:K,3)
  for(n in 1:N){
    a=sample(1:3,1)
    b=sample(10*(doctop[d,a]-1)+1:10,1)
    w[d,n,b]=1
  }
}

phi=array(0,dim=c(D,N,K))
lamb=matrix(sample(1:4,K*V,replace=T),K,V)
r=0.8
nliter=10
niter=100
for(iter in 1:niter){
  d=sample(1:D,1)
  gamm[d,]=1
  for(liter in 1:nliter){
    psi2=digamma(lamb)
    for(n in 1:N){
      psi1=digamma(gamm[d,])
      indi=which(w[d,n,]==1)
      phi[d,n,]=exp(psi1+psi2[,indi]-digamma(rowSums(lamb)))
      phi[d,n,]=phi[d,n,]/sum(phi[d,n,])
    }
    gamm[d,]=0.3+colSums(phi[d,,])
  }
  lamb_new=lamb
  for(k in 1:K){
    lamb_new[k,]=1
    for(n in 1:N){
      lamb_new[k,]=lamb_new[k,]+D*phi[d,n,k]*w[d,n,]
    }
  }
  lamb=lamb*(1-r)+lamb_new*r
}
plot(1:K,gamm[2,])

plot(1:K,gamm[8,])

plot(1:K,gamm[4,])

plot(1:K,gamm[7,])
